{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1317729, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 259201, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "草，消费税，爷税务DNA动了", "timestamp": 1616494285, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1323274, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 259201, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "考虑一个市场，存在三种货币，A、B和C。A和B不能兑换，但分别可以以6:1兑换成C，而C可以1：1任意兑换成A或B，如果C不能直接消费，那么A，B两种货币怎么说", "timestamp": 1616577649, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1323601, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 259201, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 没有理解到呢？A和B有区别吗？", "timestamp": 1616581830, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1323797, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 259201, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 这是fixed还是float…？", "timestamp": 1616583706, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1323801, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 259201, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: （哪些汇率是市场决定的", "timestamp": 1616583724, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1349274, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 259201, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "是不是存在套利空间呢 这是不稳定的系统吧", "timestamp": 1616935511, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1349277, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 259201, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 回复Bob", "timestamp": 1616935529, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1349682, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 259201, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有没有人回答我的问题啊", "timestamp": 1616939321, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1354826, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 259201, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "A和B是两个国家嘛？直觉是B加税会影响实际GDP所以B国贬值，然而是不是还得回去查查书。。。（欢迎讨论", "timestamp": 1617011170, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1354840, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 259201, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如果你说的真的是一个市场的话…每个用B支付的交易都要被抽掉10%的税，如果B没有个央行的话B的货币量不就越来越少了…", "timestamp": 1617011442, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1356999, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 259201, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "是一个国家啊，流通两种货币", "timestamp": 1617032750, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1357002, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 259201, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "类似于澳门地区的情况", "timestamp": 1617032779, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1357183, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 259201, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这里说说我的主要困惑，一开始，由于B货币购买力下降，市场上比价假设变为100：110。但是由于在商店购物后，店主也需要将B货币置换为A，所以商品标价应为A100元，或B120元（店主实际收入110元，含10元的税）。但是这又导致B购买力下降，市场上AB比价变为100：120，这又导致商店标价变为100：130•••如此往复，可推导出B价值变为0", "timestamp": 1617034099, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1357188, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 259201, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "请问这个推理错在哪里", "timestamp": 1617034127, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1357386, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 259201, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "答案是什么？", "timestamp": 1617035603, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1357399, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 259201, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这和澳门有什么联系吗（", "timestamp": 1617035660, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1358489, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 259201, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 只是举例说明一个地区通行两种货币的情况", "timestamp": 1617069474, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1358638, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": f